changing rapidly, and as a member of Vogue's new media, I was in the line with the train of the ages.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow do you describe your job to friends and family?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eI always tell my family members that Condé Nast is my second home and they couldn’t agree more.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eI started working at Condé Nast shortly after graduating from college and it's been almost ten years since then. I've been here for almost my entire career, so it's really an irreplaceable sense of belonging. Everyone in my family knows that I work for Vogue (The Fashion Bible). Vogue China observes culture through the lens of fashion, looks at the world today and uses the best photo, video and text production to convey our values to readers. New media is also a very important part of this and I think we are doing something amazing together.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLunar New Year is approaching soon, what does this holiday mean to you and how do you plan to celebrate?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eMy family's tradition is that the entire extended family stays together for the Lunar New Year. It's a very high-quality time to spend together as a family. So basically, the entire holiday season is filled with family visits, with all the relatives going around and paying New Year's greetings to each other. My parents cook very well, so my stomach will always be full during the New Year.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\