's important to capture the attention of the public and the market while maintaining a high level of creativity on a daily basis. The big tentpole events are such highlights through which we connect almost all of our partners - the most influential celebrities, supermodels, photographers, brand clients and readers that Vogue China works with, and it becomes an important program for us.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eIt was also an opportunity to showcase the results of our major projects, such as the aforementioned projects, at the big tentpole events, giving the public and the market a more comprehensive view of the “Vogue China Universe.” This is also reflected in the data, as each big tentpole event generates a huge amount of exposure, measured in billions of dollars, with a high level of social media discussion and engagement, and a significant increase in followers.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eYou also lead digital channels for the brand. What is something that you are currently working on that will help lead with the progression of those channels?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eEverything is changing so fast in China. There are so many digital/social media platforms in China and the environment is changing so fast that we need to keep an eye on the content and operation strategies of different social media platforms. We keep in touch with the official staff of all the platforms for a long time and with high frequency.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eIn terms of content, in addition to the content produced by Vogue digital itself, I will also work with other editorial teams at Vogue China to continue to create better IPs that are more engaging for our readers. New media is the most intuitive and timely way to synchronize with readers' feedback, so I will also work with other teams such as the consumer team and the digital team to analyze readers' data and profiles more accurately as support. We also need to focus on what's happening on social media, so my friends love to talk to me about what's going on and they are all surprised about how I know everything. I say, “Because I'm doing new media.”\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat can we expect to see from the brand in 2024?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003e2024 continues to be a challenging and exciting year. We will continue to do Vogue China’s influential annual projects this year and I believe it will be more mature. At the same time, more projects will arrive, such as Vogue House, which will be launched in 2024. As our Vogue China audience seeks to be more immersed in the brand, we will “come home” to Beijing in the spring 2024 to a standalone house in Beijing with a history to match Vogue’s 131-year legacy.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eThis is where our members enter Vogue’s world, brought to life off the page, an ever-evolving curation of culture and offline storytelling through the lens of fashion.Vogue House Beijing is a world-first, always-on offline destination for our engaged community. I'm looking forward to being able to officially see it. In the meantime, I'm looking forward to more changes happening in the digital world!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\"\u003eFinally, I wish you all a happy new year!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u0